"Safe" is open, open is with the flaps parallel to air stream from
turbine. Spring pulls open.

Warming the engine faster allows the engine to wear for a shorter time
while cold, this is true in San Francisco, Phoenix, Minneapolis as
well as many other locations on the planet.

